0220 GLM11A: IOLIST R0$(1),R1$(1)
0230 GLM21A: IOLIST S0$(1),S1$(1)
0240 GLM04A: IOLIST X$(1)
0250 GLM02A: IOLIST X0$(1),A[ALL],U[ALL]
